data.name: ModuleHelp.Text
data.value: A module to edit education program profile

data.name: labelProfileCode.Help
data.value: Enter the code of an educational program profile according to standard.

data.name: labelProfileTitle.Help
data.value: Enter the title for an educational program profile, defined in standard.

data.name: labelLanguages.Help
data.value: Enter the list of IETF language tags in "xx" or "xx-YY" format (e.g. "en"), separated by semicolon (;).

data.name: labelIsAdopted.Help
data.value: Check if the edu. program (profile) is adopted for peoples with disabilities.

data.name: labelEduLevel.Help
data.value: Select the education level from the dropdown.

data.name: labelEduProgramLevel.Help
data.value: Select educational program level from the dropdown.

data.name: labelEduProgram.Help
data.value: Select the educational program to which the profile belongs.

data.name: labelAccreditedToDate.Help
data.value: Enter the date until current educational program profile was accredited to.

data.name: labelCommunityAccreditedToDate.Help
data.value: Enter the date until current educational program profile was accredited to by community.

data.name: labelStartDate.Help
data.value: Enter the date from current educational program profile should be published on the site.

data.name: labelEndDate.Help
data.value: Enter the date from current educational program profile should be removed from publication on the site.

data.name: labelDivision.Help
data.value: Select division, which relates to the educational program profile. Generally it's a producting department of a faculty.

data.name: labelAudit.Help
data.value: Audit data for the educational program profile.
